<item>
 <title>Душа трепещет без тепла</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/stih/dusha-trepeshchet-bez-tepla</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/stih/dusha-trepeshchet-bez-tepla&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://vse.la/images/styles/thumb180/public/stihi_images/2369.jpg?itok=dVQw3cVx&quot; width=&quot;180&quot; height=&quot;127&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0000FF&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Застыв в оцепененье, тихо мыслю, &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0000FF&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Скольжу за образом, слепой мечтой,&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

